# GEX Regime Intelligence — Kill Chain Layer

**Status: ✅ VALIDATED & WIRED — GEX predicts vol (p<0.0001), combined with COT = 73.4% 20d WR.**

## Data Source

- **Origin**: Options chain data via `yfinance` → Put/Call ratios, Open Interest, Max Pain
- **Proxy**: `inst_context.gamma_pressure` (0-1 normalized), computed by `GammaExposureTracker`
- **Freshness**: Real-time during RTH (options data updates intraday)
- **Component**: `live_monitoring/exploitation/gamma_tracker.py`

## Backtest Results (2018–2026, N=2,051 trading days)

### Core Finding: GEX Predicts REGIME, Not Direction

| Regime | N | 5d Return | 5d Win | 20d Return | Fwd Vol | Tail Risk |
|--------|---|-----------|--------|------------|---------|-----------|
| Strong Pos GEX | 1,130 | +0.21% | 61.3% | +0.70% | 10.9% | 8.7% |
| Mild Pos GEX | 746 | +0.27% | 60.7% | +1.33% | 17.1% | 31.0% |
